cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper deals with computer vision tasks such as contour detection and semantic labeling, which are typically categorized under cs.CV. The paper also extensively uses deep learning techniques, which are commonly associated with cs.LG and cs.AI. The use of sparse coding and transfer learning also suggests possible categories of cs.NE and cs.MM.
